    "We display the results of our test in Table C.1.",
    "While we find more overlap than random draws, the effect is not large.",
    "Even in the most egregious case, there is only a 0.04 difference in absolute IoU.",
    "As such, we believe the two different test sets measure distinct generalization aspects.",
